: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;\">📞 Call Us Now</a>\n            <a href=\"mailto:{{ $credentials.business_email }}\" style=\"background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;\">✉️ Email Us</a>\n        </div>\n        \n        <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #666; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 20px;\">\n            If you're no longer interested, please <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #667eea;\">click here to unsubscribe</a>.\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
